# Using the Alfajores Testnet
The Alfajores testnet is Celo’s developer-friendly environment for testing dApps. It mirrors the Mainnet but uses testnet tokens.

## Steps
1. Get testnet Celo Gold from the [Alfajores faucet](https://faucet.celo.org).
2. Configure your project’s network settings in `hardhat.config.js` or `truffle-config.js`:
   ```javascript
   module.exports = {
     networks: {
       alfajores: {
         url: "https://alfajores-forno.celo-testnet.org",
         accounts: [YOUR_PRIVATE_KEY]
       }
     }
   };
